ief Finance Officer, and Binod Kumar Das as Cricket Manager with effect from January 1, 2021.","title":"Dav Whatmore appointed Nepali cricket Head Coach - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/17/149669/","video":[]}
